<paragraph blockId="6.[151,1436,151,428]" pageId="6" pageNumber="548">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,315,151,177]" pageId="6" pageNumber="548">Remarks.</emphasis>
The species was firstly reported as 
<taxonomicName authority="Huang, 1981" authorityName="Huang" authorityYear="1981" box="[699,1118,151,177]" class="Insecta" family="Acrididae" genus="Tenuifemurus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="548" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="curticerca">
